The paper deals with text-to-SQL generation, which involves natural language processing and database querying. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves database querying, which suggests the category cs.DB (Databases). The use of deep learning models for text-to-SQL generation suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves classification and prediction tasks, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval tasks, which suggests the category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
